.TH WORM 6 "The University of Arizona \- 8/12/84"
.SH NAME
worm \- display random worm on the Chromatics CG 3999
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f3worm [\f3\-b\fIn\f3 \-s\fIn\f3 \-f\fIn\f3 \-l\fIn\f3 \-r\fIn\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fIWorm\fR displays the movement of a random worm on the Chromatics
CG 3999
color graphics terminal.
The following options may be given in any order:
.sp 1
.nf
.ta .75i
\f3\-b\fIn\fR	set background color (0\-7, default: 1 {blue})
\f3\-c\fIn\fR	set duration of display (default: 1000)
\f3\-f\fIn\fR	set foreground color (0\-7, default: 7 {white})
\f3\-l\fIn\fR	set length of worm (default: 10)
\f3\-r\fIn\fR	set random number seed (default: 0)
.fi
